title My Notifications Page Sequence

User->Notifications_Block: open /my-dam/my-notifications
Notifications_Block->Notifications_Client: loadBlendedMessages()
Notifications_Client->Messages_API: GET /api/messages?locale=<currentLocale>
Messages_API->Notifications_API: listNotifications()
Notifications_API->MESSAGES_KV: list + get user notifications
Notifications_API->EDS_Sheet: fetch /{locale}/system-notifications
Notifications_API-->Notifications_Client: merged messages[]
Notifications_Client-->Notifications_Block: messages[]
Notifications_Block->LocalStorage: cleanup read/deleted SYSTEM ids
Notifications_Block->Notifications_Block: remove deleted SYSTEM messages
Notifications_Block->Notifications_Block: sort + filter + render + update badge

opt user marks message as read
  User->Notifications_Block: expand unread row
  Notifications_Block->Notifications_Client: markAsRead(message)
  alt owner == SYSTEM
    Notifications_Client->LocalStorage: add SYSTEM read id
  else owner != SYSTEM
    Notifications_Client->Messages_API: POST /api/messages/:id {status: "read"}
  end
end

opt user deletes message
  User->Notifications_Block: click delete and confirm
  Notifications_Block->Notifications_Client: deleteMessage(message)
  alt owner == SYSTEM
    Notifications_Client->LocalStorage: add SYSTEM deleted id
  else owner != SYSTEM
    Notifications_Client->Messages_API: DELETE /api/messages/:id
  end
end

opt expired cleanup run
  Notifications_Block->Notifications_Client: deleteMessages(expiredMessages)
  Notifications_Block->Notifications_Block: refresh list and badge
end
